decision_details:
- the proposal made by H.E. the President in his capacity as the Minister of Highways, Ports and Shipping to award the contracts  for the rehabilitation and improvements to the following road sections under the above project as recommended by the Standing Cabinet Appointed Procurement Committee (SCAPC), was approved by the Cabinet:

* Ambalangoda - Elpitiya - Pitigala Road (B14) from 16.23 km to 29.36 km;

* Hendala - Hunupitiya Road (B151)
	from  0.00 km to 4.02 km;

* Kotte  - Bope Road (B240) from 0.00 km to 3.70 km
 	and Battaramulla - Pannipitiya Road (B47) from 0.00 km to 3.50 km;

* Pelmadulla - Embilipitiya - Nonagama Road (A18) from	66.26 km to 87.69 km;

* Medawachchiya - Horowpathana Road (B282)
	from 0.00 km to 10.00 km; and

* Matale - Wattegama Road (B462) from 0.00 km to 13.00 km.
